bush carpenter
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a self-trained rough carpenter; a carpenter without formal training; a rough carpenter
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: cf. bush lawyer, bush philosopher
